      <title>私人信贷基金正在洽谈融资收购 Trivium Packaging</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/private-credit-funds-in-talks-to-finance-acquisition-of-trivium</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，私人信贷基金正在制定计划，提供高达 25 亿美元的资金，为出售美国包装公司 Trivium Packaging 提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/private-credit-funds-in-talks-to-finance-acquisition-of-trivium</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:52:12 GMT</pubDate>
