    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示美联储有时间用数据来指导决策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/powell-says-fed-has-time-for-data-to-guide-decisions-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示：“我们认为，在我们对通胀持续下降至 2% 更有信心之前，降低政策利率并不合适。”鲍威尔周三在斯坦福大学商业、政府和社会论坛上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/powell-says-fed-has-time-for-data-to-guide-decisions-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:29:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示美联储在决定降息之前有时间评估数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/powell-says-fed-has-time-to-assess-data-before-deciding-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，政策制定者将等待更明显的通胀下降迹象，然后再降息，尽管最近的物价上涨并没有改变其更广泛的轨迹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/powell-says-fed-has-time-to-assess-data-before-deciding-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利电信在法庭胜诉后有望获得 10 亿欧元的意外收获</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/telecom-italia-may-get-back-1-billion-from-italy-after-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马上诉法院在一桩可追溯至 90 年代末的法律案件中做出了有利于曾经的垄断者的裁决后，Telecom Italia SpA 预计将从意大利政府获得约 10 亿欧元（合 11 亿美元）的意外收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/telecom-italia-may-get-back-1-billion-from-italy-after-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 15:10:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普SPAC投资者在内幕交易案中认罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-spac-investor-pleads-guilty-to-insider-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名被指控在空白支票公司进行内幕交易的投资者承认了一项证券欺诈罪，该公司将唐纳德·特朗普的社交媒体初创公司公开化，距离审判不到一个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-spac-investor-pleads-guilty-to-insider-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>棕榈滩精英筹集资金吸引范德比尔特到佛罗里达</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/palm-beach-elite-are-raising-money-to-lure-vanderbilt-to-florida</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富裕的佛罗里达州居民和开发商正在寻求为范德比尔特大学筹集至少 3 亿美元，以在西棕榈滩建造一个庞大的校园。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/palm-beach-elite-are-raising-money-to-lure-vanderbilt-to-florida</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:39:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄页所有者寻求 3.5 亿美元的私人信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/yellow-pages-owner-seeks-350-million-of-private-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，拥有黄页的软件公司 Thryv Holdings Inc. 已与私人信贷机构讨论了 3.5 亿美元的资金，为其现有债务再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/yellow-pages-owner-seeks-350-million-of-private-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:01:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示美联储在降息之前还有时间，金价接近 2,300 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/gold-hits-record-as-silver-surges-on-outlook-for-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔暗示政策制定者将等待通胀下降的更明显迹象后再降息，金价升至另一纪录高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/gold-hits-record-as-silver-surges-on-outlook-for-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 01:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
